func:
var PQA             = global.get("PQA.Real_Time_Parameters",'memoryOnly')   || null;
var C2S             = global.get("C2S",'memoryOnly')                        || null;
var DownHoleData    = global.get('DownHoleData','memoryOnly')               || null;

var date            = new Date();

// Date
var year            = date.getFullYear();
var month           = date.getMonth()+1;
var day             = date.getDate();

//Time
var hours           = date.getHours();
var minutes         = date.getMinutes();
var seconds         = date.getSeconds();

msg.payload = {
    'fecha_hora'                : year+'/'+month+'/'+day+" "+hours+':'+minutes+':'+seconds,
    'Frequency'                 : PQA != null && typeof PQA.Frequency                                          != 'undefined' ? parseFloat(PQA.Frequency).toFixed(3):"--",
